data.description: Welcome to 1311 James Street. This spacious 3-bedroom ranch in Monroeville has so much to offer. Tons of natural light,2 fireplaces Large 2-part family room that has its own kitchen! Imagine the family that likes to host parties or Holiday get togethers. You can do all of your cooking in the downstairs and not worry about disturbing your living space! The upstairs has the Livingroom and bathroom and kitchen as well as 3 nice size bedrooms with original hardwood floors throughout. Wait! don't forget to take a look at the fenced in backyard as well as parking that can hold up to 10 cars!   Don't let this home pass you by!
